name: VIDEO_SOURCE_REJOIN_CHANNEL_SUCCESS
description:
Occurs when a user rejoins the channel.When a user loses connection with the server because of network problems, the SDK automatically tries to reconnect and triggers this callback upon reconnection.
        The callback for the second instance.

parameters.uid: The ID of the user who rejoins the channel.

parameters.elapsed: Time elapsed (ms) from starting to reconnect until the SDK triggers this callback.
